# AMR D convergence Poiseuille with a vertical X band, scale 1 template.

Simulation amr_d_poiseuille_xband_scale1 D2Q9

Define scale = 1
Define Fx = 5e-5
Define omega = 1.0
Define rho0 = 1.0

Domain L = 18 x 14  N = 18 x 14
Physics nu = 0.16666666666666666 Fx = 5e-5

Boundary west periodic
Boundary east periodic
Boundary south wall
Boundary north wall

Refine xband { region = [6, 0, 12, 14], ratio = 2 }

Run 80 steps
Diagnostics every 20 [step, ux, uy]
